* '''''Lowest score:''''' 3.6 (24) against [[St Kilda Football Club|St Kilda]] at Etihad Stadium on 22 July 2011
* '''''Longest winning streak:''''' 10 games (Rounds 13â22, 2005)
* '''''Longest losing streak:''''' 10 games (Round 18 1999 to Round 5 2000)
* '''''Largest home attendance:''''' 51,140 against [[Port Adelaide Football Club|Port Adelaide]] at AAMI Stadium on 26 April 2003
* '''''Largest attendance:''''' 99,645 against [[St Kilda Football Club|St Kilda]] at the [[Melbourne Cricket Ground]] â 1997 Grand Final
* '''''Most Goals in a Game''''': Tony Modra 13 goals vs Richmond (1993), Tony Modra 13 goals vs Carlton (1994)
* '''''Largest Winning Margin''''': 139 points â Round 16, 1993 v Richmond at Football Park
* '''''Largest Losing Margin''''': 141 points â Round 17, 2004 v Brisbane at Gabba
